PowerPC

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


PowerPC

Designer
AIM


Bits
32-bit/64-bit (32 → 64)


Introduced
1992; 25 years ago (1992)


Version
2.02


Design
RISC


Type
Load-store


