All-in-One Panel PC Systems
All-in-One (AIO) computers, also known as Panel PCs, are self-contained platforms that combine the computer and display into the same case. AIO systems are available in a variety of forms such as Heavy Industrial Panel PCs, Fanless PCs, Digital Signage Systems, Open Frame Panel PCs, and PoE Panel PCs.




 
All-in-One (AIO) computers, also known as Panel PCs, are self-contained platforms that combine the computer and display into the same case. AIO systems are available in a variety of forms such as Heavy Industrial Panel PCs, Fanless PCs, Slim AIOs, Digital Signage systems, Open Frame Panel PCs, and PoE Panel PCs.
Light Duty Panel PCsLight Duty Panel PCs deliver consistent performance and are designed for reliable operation in controlled environments.  These systems feature sleek modern designs and add-on features such as Magnetic Stripe and RFID readers.  Light Duty Panel computers are ideally suited for KIOSK, point-of-sale (POS), and digital signage applications in office buildings, schools, hotels, and retail stores.







