Digital Signage SystemsEnoch Digital Signage Computers are specifically engineered to meet the unique needs of the digital signage industry.  Our Digital Signage Computers feature very unique mounting solutions that will allow them to be installed in virtually any type of wall surface, from drywall to glass. These systems also feature Power over Ethernet technology, which eliminates the need for nearby AC outlets and simplifies how power is delivered to these digital signs. Optional LED side indicator lights can be programmed to display different colors to denote different statuses.  For example in a room scheduling application, green could denote that a room is available and red when it’s occupied.







