Open Frame Panel PCsEnoch OpenPanel systems are highly integrated computing solutions that combine computing and display technology into an open frame module.  These open frame modules were created to be used as building block and help engineers quickly develop their products and decrease their time-to-market.  OpenPanel was designed for manufacturers and system integrators who develop their own products and solutions. OpenPanel is a drop in turn-key display and computing solution that engineers can use to help them quickly develop and launch new products.







